1 0 
;Fab14 was generated by cleaving IgG14 with papain.
RBD was obtained by first expressing a MBP-RBD fusion construct, followed by removal of MBP tag using TEV cleavage. A TEV cleavage site was present between MBP and RBD.
RBD-Fab14 complex was prepared by mixing both in equal molar ratio, followed by purification via SEC.
;
'RBD bound to Fab14'                         RECOMBINANT COMPLEX '1, 2, 3' ? ? 
2 1 ? 'receptor binding domain of wild-type spike' RECOMBINANT COMPLEX 3         ? ? 
3 1 ? Fab14                                        RECOMBINANT COMPLEX '1, 2'    ? ? 
